Subject: Re: [T2] resistance specs/temp 2 sender

Take a close look at where the wire goes - it it goes to a bolt head - 
you've the sender already there.

If not I would pop a valve cover off and look at the serial number.

Bet you have a '72-'74 engine that came originally with carbs and no temp 
senders.

Let us know what you find.

